### Finance API Test Examples
### Use com VS Code REST Client extension ou Postman/Insomnia

### Variables (substitua pelos valores reais)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = seu_jwt_token_aqui
@userId = 1

### 1. REGISTRO DE USUÁRIO
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 2. LOGIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. PERFIL DO USUÁRIO
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. ATUALIZAR PERFIL
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "João Silva Santos",
  "email": "joao.santos@email.com"
}

### 5. CRIAR BANCO
POST {{baseUrl}}/banks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Banco do Brasil",
  "code": "001"
}

### 6. LISTAR BANCOS
GET {{baseUrl}}/banks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. CRIAR CATEGORIA
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Supermercado",
  "description": "Compras no supermercado",
  "icon": "🛒",
  "color": "#FF6B6B",
  "type": "EXPENSE"
}

### 8. LISTAR CATEGORIAS
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. CATEGORIAS POR TIPO
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/type/EXPENSE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. CRIAR CONTA
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "bankId": 1,
  "name": "Conta Corrente Principal",
  "type": "CONTA_CORRENTE",
  "balance": 1000.00
}

### 11. LISTAR CONTAS
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. CRIAR ORÇAMENTO
POST {{baseUrl}}/budgets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Orçamento Alimentação Março",
  "amount": 800.00,
  "startDate": "2025-03-01",
  "endDate": "2025-03-31",
  "period": "MONTHLY"
}

### 13. LISTAR ORÇAMENTOS
GET {{baseUrl}}/budgets/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. CRIAR META
POST {{baseUrl}}/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "name": "Viagem para Europa",
  "description": "Economizar para viagem de férias",
  "targetAmount": 15000.00,
  "targetDate": "2025-12-31",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "icon": "✈️",
  "color": "#4ECDC4"
}

### 15. LISTAR METAS
GET {{baseUrl}}/goals/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. CRIAR TRANSAÇÃO - RECEITA
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "accountId": 1,
  "name": "Salário",
  "category": "ALIMENTACAO",
  "type": "INCOME",
  "amount": 3000.00
}

### 17. CRIAR TRANSAÇÃO - DESPESA
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "accountId": 1,
  "name": "Compra no supermercado",
  "category": "ALIMENTACAO",
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "amount": 150.50
}

### 18. LISTAR TRANSAÇÕES
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 19. TRANSAÇÕES RECENTES
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/user/{{userId}}/recent?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 20. DASHBOARD COMPLETO
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 21. ANALYTICS DO MÊS ATUAL
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/user/{{userId}}/current-month
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 22. ANALYTICS PERSONALIZADO
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/user/{{userId}}?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-03-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 23. NOTIFICAÇÕES NÃO LIDAS
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/user/{{userId}}/unread
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 24. CONTADOR DE NOTIFICAÇÕES
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/user/{{userId}}/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 25. MARCAR NOTIFICAÇÃO COMO LIDA
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 26. ATUALIZAR PROGRESSO DA META
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/goals/1/progress?amount=500.00
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 27. ATUALIZAR CONTA
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Conta Corrente Atualizada"
}

### 28. DELETAR TRANSAÇÃO
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transactions/1/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 29. DELETAR CONTA
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 30. DOCUMENTAÇÃO SWAGGER
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger-ui.html

### 31. API DOCS JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/api-docs

### 32. HEALTH CHECK
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health